venue.name: Spark Bureau
venue.accessibility: Access to Spark Bureau is by way of stairwell. Please advise us of your needs and we will accommodate you.
venue.under_18: We are a Youth Node and will provide a child Safe environment. Guardians must ensure safety to and from events.
venue.childcare: We welcome parents and carers at the event. Please advise us of your needs and we will accommodate you.
venue.public_transport: Sunshine Plaza is the nearest public transport.
venue.parking: There is limited parking on Ocean Street so we are looking into what we can do to accommodate you better. Check back for details ahead of the event.

catering: Catering will be provided. More details to come on Friday 29th July. Please advise us if you have any special dietary requirements.
